<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .delv-head {
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 1.2;
        text-transform: none;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .delv-speach {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.4;
        text-transform: none;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .delv-close {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-transform: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .delv-comp {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-transform: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img src="<YOUR LOGO URL>" height="42" width="112" />
      <p class="delv-head">Howdy,</p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        We're thrilled to share with you an exclusive offer from the team here at <YOUR COMPANY>. As a token of our gratitude for your continued support, we're providing a 15% discount on any of our construction or renovation services.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        Whether you're considering a small upgrade to freshen up your home or planning a comprehensive renovation project, our team of experts is ready to bring your vision to life. And with this special discount, there's never been a better time to transform your space.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        To claim your 15% discount, simply visit our website at <a href="<WEBSITE URL>">THE HYPER LINK</a> and the discount will automatically be applied to your next project.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        Your trust and satisfaction have always been at the heart of what we do at <YOUR COMPANY>. Thank you for allowing us to serve you, and we look forward to helping you create the space of your dreams.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        Here's to building a better home, together.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-close">Best regards,</p>
      <p class="delv-close">garrett is such a bro</p>
      <p class="delv-comp">YOUR COMPANY PHONE NUMBER</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>